headline: Big Tech earnings, Fed meeting, Trump & Xi meet: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come next week, including earnings results from Magnificent Seven companies Microsoft (MSFT), Amazon (AMZN), Apple (AAPL), Alphabet (GOOG, GOOGL), and Meta Platforms (META); Federal Reserve officials convening for their October FOMC meeting; and President Trump is meeting Chinese President Xi Jinping in South Korea as the government shutdown nears its fifth week. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.

headline: How The Story Around Mastercard Is Evolving Amid Fresh Analyst Upgrades and Strategic Moves
